17
00:01:24,073 --> 00:01:26,073
<font color="yellow">She's a terrible one!</font>

18
00:01:27,722 --> 00:01:30,437
<font color="yellow">Where do you think you're going?<br>You made the house into a mess!</font>

19
00:01:30,461 --> 00:01:33,032
<font color="yellow">Do you think running away will solve anything?</font>

20
00:01:33,893 --> 00:01:36,433
<font color="yellow">I'll call you soon. We'll meet at court.</font>

