22
00:01:38,744 --> 00:01:41,309
<font color="yellow">Why do we have to meet at court?</font>

23
00:01:42,026 --> 00:01:45,564
<font color="yellow">I did nothing wrong! All I did was<br>have our kids and raise them!</font>

24
00:01:47,963 --> 00:01:49,323
