27
00:01:56,752 --> 00:01:59,645
<font color="yellow">So what did you find out?<br>What did I do? You tell me!</font>

28
00:02:00,323 --> 00:02:02,228
<font color="yellow">Well...</font>

29
00:02:02,252 --> 00:02:03,252
<font color="yellow">Look here!</font>

30
00:02:04,050 --> 00:02:09,981
<font color="yellow">Was Chung-ja the one who had an affair?<br>You get angry at others for your mistakes!</font>

31
00:02:10,753 --> 00:02:13,436
<font color="yellow">You should be begging for<br>forgiveness on your knees! How dare you</font>

32
00:02:13,461 --> 00:02:16,143
