33
00:02:18,472 --> 00:02:22,058
<font color="yellow">- You little...<br>- Jo Dal-ho!</font>

34
00:02:23,081 --> 00:02:29,777
<font color="yellow">- What do I do?<br>- My goodness! I'm so upset!</font>

35
00:02:31,198 --> 00:02:34,994
<font color="yellow">But who sent you these pictures?</font>

36
00:02:35,557 --> 00:02:39,025
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja, did you really<br>hire someone to take these?</font>

37
00:02:39,581 --> 00:02:43,091
<font color="yellow">I didn't do this. I wonder who did it.</font>

38
00:02:52,369 --> 00:02:54,664
<font color="yellow">Did you take these photos?</font>

39
00:02:55,665 --> 00:02:56,665
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

40
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,664
<font color="yellow">I was so upset that people<br>misunderstood you as having</font>

41
00:02:59,688 --> 00:03:01,829
<font color="yellow">delusional suspicion of<br>your husband's faithfulness.</font>

42
00:03:02,631 --> 00:03:07,969
<font color="yellow">But I think I made a mistake. Father was<br>so angry when he left. What will we do now?</font>

43
00:03:08,688 --> 00:03:10,625
<font color="yellow">No, no. You did the right thing.</font>

44
00:03:11,728 --> 00:03:14,656
<font color="yellow">If it wasn't for you, I would've<br>continued to be a mental patient.</font>

45
00:03:15,414 --> 00:03:18,736
<font color="yellow">You did the right thing by<br>proving I'm a sane person.</font>

46
00:03:19,236 --> 00:03:22,283
<font color="yellow">Thank you, Shin-ae. You did the right thing.</font>

47
00:03:24,047 --> 00:03:28,267
<font color="yellow">Mother, are you going to just let this slide?</font>

48
00:03:29,025 --> 00:03:30,025
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

49
00:03:30,329 --> 00:03:33,563
<font color="yellow">You should barge into<br>Mi-poong's house with your friends.</font>

50
00:03:33,587 --> 00:03:36,886
<font color="yellow">Show them these photos<br>and turn that house upside down.</font>

51
00:03:37,344 --> 00:03:40,032
<font color="yellow">Make sure they can't live in that<br>neighborhood without any shame.</font>

52
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:44,680
<font color="yellow">You're right. I have these photos as proof.</font>

53
00:03:45,985 --> 00:03:49,964
<font color="yellow">I'm going to make sure to<br>chase them out of Geum-sil's house</font>

54
00:03:49,990 --> 00:03:53,534
<font color="yellow">so that they can't come near us ever again.</font>

55
00:04:02,353 --> 00:04:04,940
<font color="yellow">- What are these?<br>- Can't you tell?</font>

56
00:04:08,797 --> 00:04:11,601
<font color="yellow">So your husband really cheated on you?</font>

57
00:04:12,688 --> 00:04:13,945
<font color="yellow">It's so unfair.</font>

58
00:04:14,875 --> 00:04:19,851
<font color="yellow">Soon-jung, I'm about to lose<br>my husband to a fox, just like you did.</font>

59
00:04:21,618 --> 00:04:23,765
<font color="yellow">- What am I supposed to do?<br>- What else?</font>

60
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:27,469
<font color="yellow">Let's go. Chung-ja, lead the way.</font>

61
00:04:27,923 --> 00:04:32,719
<font color="yellow">- Go where?<br>- Evil home-wreckers like her must be crushed!</font>

62
00:04:34,017 --> 00:04:36,902
<font color="yellow">What are you guys doing?<br>She's about to lose her husband!</font>

63
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:40,429
