<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>

65
00:04:44,453 --> 00:04:48,140
<font color="yellow">Get up and eat this<br>so that you can feel better.</font>

66
00:04:49,203 --> 00:04:52,452
<font color="yellow">I feel nauseous!</font>

67
00:04:52,563 --> 00:04:55,969
<font color="yellow">Why did you drink in the first place?</font>

68
00:04:56,258 --> 00:05:00,078
<font color="yellow">Why would you do something<br>you've never done before at this age?</font>

69
00:05:00,837 --> 00:05:01,837
<font color="yellow">Here.</font>

70
00:05:03,462 --> 00:05:06,399
<font color="yellow">My goodness. Serves you right.</font>

71
00:05:07,197 --> 00:05:08,813
<font color="yellow">Aren't you going to go to work?</font>

72
00:05:09,626 --> 00:05:11,548
<font color="yellow">I'm really going to quit.</font>

73
00:05:11,828 --> 00:05:13,921
<font color="yellow">Oh, be quiet!</font>

74
00:05:13,945 --> 00:05:16,936
