77
00:05:22,179 --> 00:05:23,304
<font color="yellow">Do you still want me to go?</font>

78
00:05:23,594 --> 00:05:27,486
<font color="yellow">Your boss likes Geum-sil?</font>

79
00:05:28,743 --> 00:05:31,609
<font color="yellow">Father, why isn't Nam-yi here again?</font>

80
00:05:32,423 --> 00:05:34,313
<font color="yellow">Did you nag her again?</font>

81
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:37,298
