82
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:40,296
<font color="yellow">She's sick? How is she sick?</font>

83
00:05:42,650 --> 00:05:43,774
<font color="yellow">Hello, ma'am.</font>

84
00:05:44,164 --> 00:05:45,164
<font color="yellow">- Hi.<br>- Hello.</font>

85
00:05:45,782 --> 00:05:48,169
<font color="yellow">- Hi.<br>- Is Nam-yi very sick?</font>

86
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:50,178
<font color="yellow">Yes, she is.</font>

87
00:05:50,203 --> 00:05:51,486
<font color="yellow">Did she go to the hospital?</font>

88
00:05:51,931 --> 00:05:56,780
<font color="yellow">Won-bin, I came to talk to your father.</font>

89
00:05:57,188 --> 00:05:59,234
<font color="yellow">Can you go outside for a moment?</font>

90
00:05:59,258 --> 00:06:03,094
<font color="yellow">- Sure. Please tell Nam-yi to get well soon.<br>- I will.</font>

91
00:06:03,697 --> 00:06:04,738
<font color="yellow">Please have a seat.</font>

92
00:06:09,837 --> 00:06:12,712
<font color="yellow">How is Nam-yi sick?</font>

93
00:06:13,447 --> 00:06:15,899
<font color="yellow">She was fine yesterday,<br>but she suddenly said she was sick.</font>

94
00:06:16,150 --> 00:06:17,150
<font color="yellow">That's not it.</font>

95
00:06:18,164 --> 00:06:20,943
<font color="yellow">I came because I wanted to ask you something.</font>

96
00:06:22,611 --> 00:06:25,695
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim, do you like my daughter-in-law?</font>

97
00:06:27,517 --> 00:06:29,203
<font color="yellow">Yes, I like her.</font>

98
00:06:30,469 --> 00:06:33,327
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear. I didn't think you were that kind</font>

99
00:06:33,354 --> 00:06:36,275
<font color="yellow">of person. Do you think this makes any sense?</font>

100
00:06:37,344 --> 00:06:39,820
<font color="yellow">Is it wrong for me to like Geum-sil?</font>

101
00:06:40,688 --> 00:06:44,695
<font color="yellow">She resembles my biological sister.<br>That's why I like her.</font>

102
00:06:45,712 --> 00:06:51,171
<font color="yellow">So you like her as a sister<br>and not as a woman?</font>

103
00:06:51,743 --> 00:06:55,359
<font color="yellow">After my parents passed away early,<br>my sister took care of me like I was her own son.</font>

104
00:06:56,056 --> 00:06:59,779
<font color="yellow">She passed away before she could<br>see me succeed, and that broke my heart.</font>

105
00:07:00,486 --> 00:07:03,743
<font color="yellow">I really wanted to see<br>my sister, but Ms. Hwang</font>

106
00:07:03,769 --> 00:07:07,296
<font color="yellow">resembles her a lot,<br>so I was happy to just see her.</font>

107
00:07:07,322 --> 00:07:11,453
<font color="yellow">So you really like her as a sister?</font>

108
00:07:11,556 --> 00:07:16,032
<font color="yellow">Yes. However, I can end up<br>liking her as a woman.</font>

109
00:07:16,058 --> 00:07:18,020
<font color="yellow">Oh, you can't do that!</font>

110
00:07:18,203 --> 00:07:22,102
<font color="yellow">Don't even say that!<br>Just like her as a sister!</font>

111
00:07:23,298 --> 00:07:28,739
<font color="yellow">Do you know the age gap<br>between you and Geum-sil?</font>

112
00:07:29,102 --> 00:07:33,712
<font color="yellow">Men and women must meet<br>people near their own age.</font>

113
00:07:33,892 --> 00:07:37,688
<font color="yellow">When there's a huge age gap,<br>life gets very difficult.</font>

114
00:07:37,712 --> 00:07:41,952
<font color="yellow">You shouldn't meet older women.<br>Find someone your own age.</font>

115
00:07:42,212 --> 00:07:46,578
<font color="yellow">If you look around you, you'll be<br>able to find a woman around your age.</font>

116
00:07:46,804 --> 00:07:50,500
<font color="yellow">Why would you look for an older woman?</font>

117
00:07:50,806 --> 00:07:52,330
<font color="yellow">Who are you talking about?</font>

118
00:07:52,657 --> 00:07:59,361
<font color="yellow">Someone near you.<br>Someone you'll be able to meet every day.</font>

119
00:07:59,664 --> 00:08:05,287
<font color="yellow">When you think about those things,<br>someone will pop into your mind automatically.</font>

120
00:08:10,789 --> 00:08:11,789
<font color="yellow">What's this?</font>

121
00:08:12,322 --> 00:08:13,402
<font color="yellow">Fermented soybean paste.</font>

122
00:08:14,633 --> 00:08:17,299
<font color="yellow">My mother-in-law made it. If you just put</font>

123
00:08:17,325 --> 00:08:20,179
<font color="yellow">kimchi and tofu in there, it'll be delicious.</font>

124
00:08:20,322 --> 00:08:23,674
<font color="yellow">Oh, thank you! I'll enjoy it.</font>

125
00:08:24,508 --> 00:08:26,570
<font color="yellow">But did you come here just for this?</font>

126
00:08:26,789 --> 00:08:29,320
<font color="yellow">I had some time before I had<br>to go to work in the afternoon,</font>

127
00:08:29,346 --> 00:08:31,774
<font color="yellow">and I had something to tell you, too.</font>

128
00:08:31,923 --> 00:08:33,323
<font color="yellow">Something to tell me?</font>

129
00:08:34,117 --> 00:08:35,117
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

130
00:08:35,775 --> 00:08:39,399
<font color="yellow">It's about Mr. Jo's wife.</font>

131
00:08:40,087 --> 00:08:42,846
<font color="yellow">She's not allowed to come to Deokcheonok.</font>

132
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:46,406
<font color="yellow">She can't come anywhere near there anymore.</font>

133
00:08:46,664 --> 00:08:53,039
<font color="yellow">We told Mr. Kim everything<br>she had done to you.</font>

134
00:08:54,232 --> 00:09:00,303
<font color="yellow">Mr. Kim was so furious!<br>I bet Ms. Ma was scolded very badly!</font>

135
00:09:02,857 --> 00:09:03,857
<font color="yellow">I see.</font>

136
00:09:04,952 --> 00:09:10,693
<font color="yellow">So come back to Deokcheonok.<br>I came to tell you that.</font>

137
00:09:12,491 --> 00:09:17,499
<font color="yellow">Thank you. I'm very grateful...</font>

138
00:09:19,124 --> 00:09:23,029
<font color="yellow">but I don't think it would be right<br>for me to return to Deokcheonok.</font>

139
00:09:23,054 --> 00:09:27,654
<font color="yellow">- Where is this horrid wench?<br>- Hwang Geum-sil, you come out here, too!</font>

140
00:09:28,006 --> 00:09:29,169
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

141
00:09:29,342 --> 00:09:31,928
<font color="yellow">- Is it here?<br>- Break everything!</font>

142
00:09:32,976 --> 00:09:34,685
<font color="yellow">Break everything!</font>

143
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:40,225
<font color="yellow">- You horrible wench!<br>- Why are you doing this?</font>

144
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,894
<font color="yellow">Let go of me!</font>

145
00:09:43,756 --> 00:09:44,756
<font color="yellow">Oh, no!</font>

146
00:10:00,827 --> 00:10:02,563
<font color="yellow">Why are you getting in the way?</font>

147
00:10:05,452 --> 00:10:09,709
<font color="yellow">Stop, everyone! That's enough!</font>

148
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:13,684
<font color="yellow">How dare you barge into someone else's<br>home and do something so shameful!</font>

149
00:10:13,943 --> 00:10:16,271
<font color="yellow">Get out, all of you!</font>

150
00:10:17,131 --> 00:10:22,500
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja, are you crazy? Young-soon and<br>Soon-jung, why are you guys doing this, too?</font>

151
00:10:22,943 --> 00:10:25,860
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja is abnormal!</font>

152
00:10:26,124 --> 00:10:29,861
<font color="yellow">How can you not stop her from<br>doing this? Are you guys insane?</font>

153
00:10:30,202 --> 00:10:34,490
<font color="yellow">Hwang Geum-sil, are you taking<br>her side because she's your in-law?</font>

154
00:10:35,538 --> 00:10:37,874
<font color="yellow">Look at these before you speak!</font>

155
00:10:37,899 --> 00:10:39,803
<font color="yellow">- What's this?<br>- Here. Look.</font>

156
00:10:40,241 --> 00:10:42,937
<font color="yellow">What are these? My goodness.</font>

157
00:10:45,193 --> 00:10:46,193
<font color="yellow">Oh my god.</font>

158
00:10:51,991 --> 00:10:52,991
<font color="yellow">Oh my god!</font>

159
00:11:02,148 --> 00:11:04,100
<font color="yellow">What are these?</font>

160
00:11:04,264 --> 00:11:06,019
<font color="yellow">It's as you see them!</font>

161
00:11:06,044 --> 00:11:09,183
<font color="yellow">This woman seduced Chung-ja's<br>husband and had an affair with him!</font>

162
00:11:09,374 --> 00:11:10,374
<font color="yellow">No way.</font>

163
00:11:11,077 --> 00:11:15,760
<font color="yellow">How can you live with your daughter-in-law<br>whose mother is a home-wrecker?</font>

164
00:11:15,784 --> 00:11:17,102
<font color="yellow">It's not true!</font>

165
00:11:19,991 --> 00:11:24,725
<font color="yellow">No! This isn't true! It's not!</font>

166
00:11:25,857 --> 00:11:30,348
<font color="yellow">All of you, get out of here! Get out!</font>

167
00:11:30,374 --> 00:11:33,611
<font color="yellow">- Get out!<br>- It's not true!</font>

168
00:11:48,756 --> 00:11:54,380
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness. What on earth is going on?</font>

169
00:11:55,092 --> 00:11:58,323
<font color="yellow">Why would she cry when I'm the one<br>who should be crying? Hwang Geum-sil!</font>

170
00:11:58,702 --> 00:12:01,068
<font color="yellow">If you still live with<br>that woman and her daughter,</font>

171
00:12:01,093 --> 00:12:03,741
<font color="yellow">I'm going to take Hee-ra out of here.</font>

172
00:12:03,827 --> 00:12:05,898
<font color="yellow">And I won't see you ever again either!</font>

173
00:12:06,148 --> 00:12:10,414
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja, now that Geum-sil knows,<br>she'll do something about it. Let's go.</font>

174
00:12:11,178 --> 00:12:13,845
<font color="yellow">You better not tell Hee-ra about this.</font>

175
00:12:14,491 --> 00:12:16,294
<font color="yellow">Or else I'll die!</font>

176
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:19,495
<font color="yellow">Hey Hwang Geum-sil,<br>you better get your head together!</font>

177
00:12:40,232 --> 00:12:42,232
<font color="yellow">What on earth is going on?</font>

178
00:12:42,515 --> 00:12:45,685
<font color="yellow">But why did the hospital diagnose her<br>as having delusional suspicion?</font>

179
00:12:46,116 --> 00:12:49,500
<font color="yellow">You know blood pressure can<br>temporarily rise if you get excited.</font>

180
00:12:49,937 --> 00:12:54,702
<font color="yellow">She was doubtful of her husband then,<br>which is why she got that diagnosis.</font>

181
00:12:56,256 --> 00:12:58,919
<font color="yellow">But Ms. Joo really looked like<br>she was in an unfair position.</font>

182
00:12:59,788 --> 00:13:01,178
<font color="yellow">I know.</font>

183
00:13:02,023 --> 00:13:04,130
<font color="yellow">What if something went wrong?</font>

184
00:13:04,788 --> 00:13:07,446
<font color="yellow">What if they were at a push-and-pull<br>stage and got misunderstood?</font>

185
00:13:07,803 --> 00:13:10,054
<font color="yellow">What's that?</font>

186
00:13:10,374 --> 00:13:15,092
<font color="yellow">They're not going out, but they<br>might have feelings for each other.</font>

187
00:13:15,209 --> 00:13:23,160
<font color="yellow">Then you should just phrase it that way!<br>Why do you have to speak in such weird terms?</font>

188
00:13:31,467 --> 00:13:32,685
<font color="yellow">I'm back.</font>

189
00:13:51,788 --> 00:13:55,429
<font color="yellow">Out of all people, it just has<br>to be with my friend's husband.</font>

190
00:13:56,029 --> 00:13:58,866
<font color="yellow">Out of all people, it just has to be<br>with your sister-in-law's father.</font>

