262
00:19:43,755 --> 00:19:45,814
<font color="yellow">But how can she date a married man?</font>

263
00:19:46,544 --> 00:19:47,744
<font color="yellow">That's just wrong.</font>

264
00:19:48,067 --> 00:19:52,755
<font color="yellow">- You shouldn't make others miserable!<br>- My mom is not that kind of person!</font>

265
00:19:53,099 --> 00:19:59,092
