266
00:19:59,364 --> 00:20:01,802
<font color="yellow">Anyways, I can't live with either of you.</font>

267
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,896
<font color="yellow">So either you divorce Jang-go,</font>

268
00:20:05,286 --> 00:20:11,371
