269
00:20:11,817 --> 00:20:13,284
<font color="yellow">You're being too much.</font>

270
00:20:14,325 --> 00:20:16,027
<font color="yellow">Can't you believe her just this once?</font>

271
00:20:16,536 --> 00:20:18,766
<font color="yellow">Why do you keep telling me to believe her?</font>

272
00:20:20,294 --> 00:20:24,288
<font color="yellow">This is so humiliating!</font>

273
00:20:25,646 --> 00:20:29,383
