275
00:20:44,912 --> 00:20:49,255
<font color="yellow">Please believe her! Grandma! Mother! Aunt!</font>

276
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:27,224
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, I examined the photos,</font>

277
00:21:27,763 --> 00:21:29,876
<font color="yellow">and it seems like someone<br>was tailing them to take</font>

278
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:32,053
<font color="yellow">photos of them only when<br>they were closely together.</font>

279
00:21:32,832 --> 00:21:35,717
<font color="yellow">The camera was angled so that<br>they would look close to each other.</font>

280
00:21:36,457 --> 00:21:40,169
<font color="yellow">If someone was trying to trap them,<br>then they couldn't help but fall for it.</font>

281
00:21:40,982 --> 00:21:44,900
<font color="yellow">Whoever took those photos<br>is a horrible person!</font>

282
00:21:46,832 --> 00:21:48,300
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, stop crying.</font>

283
00:21:49,591 --> 00:21:53,255
<font color="yellow">Your mother must be having a hard time.<br>We should help her out, don't you think?</font>

284
00:21:57,582 --> 00:21:59,653
<font color="yellow">You're right. I'm not going to cry.</font>

285
00:22:00,872 --> 00:22:04,540
