291
00:22:18,565 --> 00:22:19,565
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

292
00:22:20,293 --> 00:22:23,802
<font color="yellow">- I'm going to get revenge.<br>- Revenge? On who?</font>

293
00:22:24,027 --> 00:22:27,865
