299
00:22:53,894 --> 00:22:56,686
<font color="yellow">You didn't answer your phone!<br>Where were you all this time?</font>

300
00:22:57,355 --> 00:22:58,715
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

301
00:22:59,457 --> 00:23:01,543
<font color="yellow">Did you fight someone today?</font>

302
00:23:02,051 --> 00:23:04,004
<font color="yellow">Yes, I did.</font>

303
00:23:04,934 --> 00:23:07,342
<font color="yellow">I dropped by Ms. Joo's house<br>before I came here.</font>

304
00:23:07,367 --> 00:23:11,880
<font color="yellow">Your wife barged into her home<br>with all her friends!</font>

305
00:23:12,267 --> 00:23:15,374
<font color="yellow">They wrecked her house<br>and pulled her hair out!</font>

306
00:23:15,855 --> 00:23:18,511
<font color="yellow">My wife went to her house?</font>

307
00:23:18,535 --> 00:23:20,471
<font color="yellow">It was so chaotic!</font>

308
00:23:20,957 --> 00:23:23,483
<font color="yellow">She showed the photos of you<br>and Ms. Joo together</font>

309
00:23:23,506 --> 00:23:25,777
<font color="yellow">and tormented her like they were after a rat!</font>

310
00:23:26,121 --> 00:23:27,121
<font color="yellow">Photos?</font>

311
00:23:27,762 --> 00:23:30,649
<font color="yellow">I'm telling you this because<br>I think you should know about it.</font>

312
00:23:32,223 --> 00:23:35,743
<font color="yellow">She worked so hard to survive after<br>coming down here from North Korea.</font>

313
00:23:36,551 --> 00:23:37,817
<font color="yellow">This is just wrong.</font>

314
00:24:05,951 --> 00:24:07,354
<font color="yellow">(Deokcheonok Boss)</font>

315
00:24:10,973 --> 00:24:13,060
<font color="yellow">Grandma, are you very sick?</font>

316
00:24:14,113 --> 00:24:16,901
<font color="yellow">I'm not sick. I'm okay now.</font>

317
00:24:18,293 --> 00:24:23,697
<font color="yellow">Yoo-sung, would you like to<br>eat some rice cakes for a snack?</font>

318
00:24:23,926 --> 00:24:24,926
<font color="yellow">Yes!</font>

319
00:24:26,105 --> 00:24:27,918
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

320
00:24:33,605 --> 00:24:34,805
<font color="yellow">Wait a little bit.</font>

321
00:25:10,176 --> 00:25:11,376
<font color="yellow">It's been a while.</font>

322
00:25:12,129 --> 00:25:15,112
<font color="yellow">Why did you come here, Mr. Jo?</font>

323
00:25:16,488 --> 00:25:21,730
<font color="yellow">- Well...<br>- Did you come here to see my mom?</font>

324
00:25:24,027 --> 00:25:30,487
