325
00:25:32,769 --> 00:25:33,769
<font color="yellow">Is she okay?</font>

326
00:25:34,363 --> 00:25:39,198
<font color="yellow">Why would you worry if she's sick or not?</font>

327
00:25:42,152 --> 00:25:47,906
<font color="yellow">- I heard she suffered because of me today...<br>- Mr. Jo.</font>

328
00:25:49,762 --> 00:25:51,418
