331
00:26:00,629 --> 00:26:03,342
<font color="yellow">Since you're acting like this, people<br>keep misunderstanding my mom,</font>

332
00:26:03,367 --> 00:26:05,581
<font color="yellow">and she keeps being humiliated like this.</font>

333
00:26:05,816 --> 00:26:09,392
<font color="yellow">How much more are you trying to<br>make her suffer by coming here?</font>

334
00:26:11,465 --> 00:26:14,737
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I'm very sorry.</font>

335
00:26:15,184 --> 00:26:18,535
<font color="yellow">If you're really sorry,<br>please don't come here.</font>

336
00:26:19,316 --> 00:26:22,650
<font color="yellow">Don't call my mom,<br>and don't be curious about her.</font>

337
00:26:23,823 --> 00:26:25,901
<font color="yellow">That's the way you can help her.</font>

338
00:26:30,090 --> 00:26:32,090
<font color="yellow">If you consider my mom at all,</font>

