00:27:18,439 --> 00:27:20,479
<font color="yellow">Hi, honey. It's me.</font>

343
00:27:22,652 --> 00:27:23,652
<font color="yellow">Right now?</font>

344
00:27:24,684 --> 00:27:26,684
<font color="yellow">Okay, I'll come out right now.</font>

345
00:27:29,277 --> 00:27:33,551
<font color="yellow">Chung-ja, have some jujube tea.</font>

346
00:27:33,575 --> 00:27:38,680
<font color="yellow">- What's going on? Where are you going?<br>- Mom, Dal-ho wants to see me outside.</font>

