351
00:28:18,374 --> 00:28:20,624
<font color="yellow">I'd rather die than divorce you.</font>

352
00:28:23,601 --> 00:28:28,101
<font color="yellow">I heard you went to Ms. Joo's house today.</font>

353
00:28:31,257 --> 00:28:35,163
