358
00:28:50,015 --> 00:28:54,082
<font color="yellow">You barged into an innocent<br>person's house and wrecked havoc.</font>

359
00:28:55,069 --> 00:28:56,564
<font color="yellow">Do you think you did the right thing?</font>

360
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:58,220
<font color="yellow">She's innocent?</font>

361
00:28:59,014 --> 00:29:02,384
<font color="yellow">I'm still alive!</font>

362
00:29:03,089 --> 00:29:06,378
<font color="yellow">Should I do nothing when<br>she seduces my husband?</font>

363
00:29:06,846 --> 00:29:10,275
