00:29:53,245 --> 00:29:56,295
<font color="yellow">I left home because of you.<br>Not because of Ms. Joo.</font>

379
00:29:58,003 --> 00:29:59,546
<font color="yellow">So don't bother her anymore.</font>

380
00:30:00,604 --> 00:30:03,792
<font color="yellow">If you bother her again...</font>

381
00:30:06,682 --> 00:30:07,829
<font color="yellow">I won't forgive you.</font>

382
00:30:08,448 --> 00:30:14,334
<font color="yellow">Did you call me out at this hour<br>just so you can tell me this?</font>

383
00:30:19,670 --> 00:30:20,670
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

