00:30:21,553 --> 00:30:25,486
<font color="yellow">If you come home,<br>I'll believe everything you just told me.</font>

385
00:30:27,155 --> 00:30:32,784
<font color="yellow">But if you don't come home,<br>I'll keep going to her house.</font>

